                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-03-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实艺术和现实的世界的区别是 艺术中是残酷中包裹着真是的人情，而现实却是虚伪的人情中半遮半掩透漏着残酷</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="561787313">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-561787313" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-561787313" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="561787313">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chilla90/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-09-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">满是充满张力的句子，写小说的人一定要看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="547017513">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-547017513" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-547017513" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="547017513">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/frank0290/">木须龙</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-06-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">战争太残酷了。一战的德国战败与二战不同，军队并没有在战场上被打垮，完全是政治因素主导了军事崩溃，尤其让人惊奇的是停战的要求竟然是军方的鲁登道夫提出的，其目的最初只是趁着尚有军事实力时与协约国体面妥协，不料人心厌战，终于满盘皆输。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

